810
00:41:02,406 --> 00:41:04,916
That you're safe.

811
00:41:04,916 --> 00:41:07,892
That you're in your bed.

812
00:41:07,892 --> 00:41:10,451
I'm home.

813
00:41:10,451 --> 00:41:13,823
