814
00:41:13,823 --> 00:41:15,961
Good.

815
00:41:15,961 --> 00:41:18,881
Okay, then.

816
00:41:18,881 --> 00:41:21,173
Let's get some rest.

817
00:41:21,173 --> 00:41:24,074
